(i) \sum_{n=1}^ \infty \frac{z^n}{3^n + 1} 
(ii) \sum_{n=1}^ \infty \frac{1}{(n + 1)z^n} 
(i)
(3^n+1))/(3^{n+1}+1)
\mod(z/3)
(ii)
((n+1)/((n+2)*z))
lim_{n\rightarrow \infty}|\frac{z^n}{3^{n+1}+1}\frac{3^n+1}{z^n}| = lim_{n\rightarrow \infty}|z|\frac{1 +\frac{1}{3^n}}{3+\frac{1}{3^n}} = \frac{|z|}{3} \Rightarrow |z|<3
\frac{1}{z} = a
lim_{n\rightarrow \infty}|\frac{a^{n+1}}{(n+1)+1}\frac{n+1}{a^n}| = lim_{n\rightarrow \infty}|a|\frac{n+1}{n+2} = |a| \Rightarrow |a| < 1
|a| = |\frac{1}{z}| < 1 \Leftrightarrow |z|>1
